overview: First show of 2013 with Jessicka Havok defending her title against Athena while Mercedes Martinez and LuFisto will want to end their rivalry. It should be noted that a significant number of women are not present at this show because blocked by snow (Allysin Kay, Sassy Stephanie, Marti Belle, Lexus, Tina San Antonio and Nikki Addams).
title: WSU An Ultraviolent Affair
